messages.ssml: <speak>It's natural to feel worried. The World Health Organization recommends we channel our concerns into action to protect ourselves, our loved ones and our communities. Wash your hands regularly. Always sneeze or cough into a tissue and wear a mask when you go out. And follow the advice of your local health authorities.</speak>
